longBusinessSummary: Vibhavadi Medical Center Public Company Limited operates a hospital under the Vibhavadi Hospital name in Thailand. It operates through two segments, Hospital and Others. The company provides medical services; and rental services and space rental. In addition, it operates an anti aging center. Vibhavadi Medical Center Public Company Limited was founded in 1986 and is based in Bangkok, Thailand.
